snippet.title: Lumo Gameplay - September 2015
snippet.description:
ESRB Rating: EVERYONE 10+ with Comic Mischief, Violent References

Lumo Gameplay trailer for the Eurogamer Expo, 2015. Lumo is being released on PC, Mac, Linux, PS4, PS Vita and XBox One on April 22nd.
